Company Overview of QMC Telecom International Holdings, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
QMC Telecom International Holdings, LLC develops, builds, and acquires cell towers in Latin America. It develops, owns, acquires, manages, and operates rooftops, macro sites. and DAS wireless infrastructure solutions in Brazil, Puerto Rico, and Mexico. The company was formerly known as QMC Telecom International Holdings Group, LLC. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in San Juan, Brazil with an additional office in Sao Paulo, Brazil.


Avenue de la Constitucion #450Condominio Torre de la ReinaSuite 203San Juan, PR 00908United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 787-721-3953

Fax: 787-625-8134

www.qmctelecom.com







