QMC Telecom International Holdings LLC

                    QMC Telecom International Holdings LLC owns and operates wireless infrastructure. It develops, owns, acquires and manages rooftops, macro sites and Distributed Antenna Systems solutions in Brazil, Colombia, Puerto Rico and Mexico. The company was founded in 2008 by Jose R. Stella and Rafael A. Somoza and is headquartered in Sao Paulo, Brazil.                  





 Other Affiliations




              Arthur Patterson is affiliated with
                            QMC Telecom International Holdings LLC.
            





